home.sub-text: Need a photographer, is it for a party, birthday, festival? Or you just want a new profile picture or photo session. It's no problem, write to me and we will certainly get along somehow.

about-me.main-text: We need to remember this as a non-professional hobby photographer, I am not a professional photographer, but I learn from my mistakes and want to be better at taking better and better photos, so that my clients are satisfied. I am Szymon and I have been interested in photography for over 5 years, and I have a two-year job experience.
